    {
        "content": "<p>Though I now remember the gap; <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=QuadraticForm.baseChange#doc\">docs#QuadraticForm.baseChange</a> works in non-free modules in characteristic not 2, whereas a proposed replacement works in any characteristic but only in free modules</p>",
        "id": 515294486,
